high_descs: Turn right and walk to the large wooden table on the left.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle to the right of the coffee maker on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Open the lower left cabinet under the sink and put the spoon on the black plate inside the cabinet.
Pick up the plate with the spoon from inside the cabinet and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter on the right.
Put the plate with the spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a spoon on a counter.

high_descs: Walk forward to the dining table in front of you.
Pick up the ladle from the table.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink.
Open the cabinet on the left below the sink and put the ladle on the plate.
Pick up the plate from the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Walk slightly to the left and turn right towards the counter top.
Put the plate on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a ladle on it on a counter top.

high_descs: go to the dining table
pick up the measuring spoon
take the spoon to the sink
put the spoon in the bowl in the cabinet to the left below the sink
pick up the bowl and spoon from the cabinet
take the bowl to the counter to the left of the sink
put the bowl on the counter
anns.task_desc: put a bowl and spoon on the counter
